"Good heavens! what a question!" exclaimed Clara, with a look of offended modesty;
                  "do you think I would have made such a confession, had I not been in the first
                  place aware of his love?"

"Rested like a king," replied he; "warm as toast; chilled at first by damp sheets;
                  soon got over it; all right at last. How are you, brother?—look rather pale. Sleep
                  well, hey?"
